name: Global X Copper Producers Index ETF
longDescription: To achieve its investment objective, COPP generally invests and holds, directly or indirectly, equity securities of the constituent issuers in substantially the same proportion as its Underlying index, the Constituent Issuers. COPP may also invest in ADRs or GDRs representing equity securities of Constituent Issuers of its Underlying Index. To the extent permitted, the ETF will generally be fully invested in or exposed to its respective Underlying Index at all times. The COPP seeks to replicate, to the extent possible and net of expenses, the performance of an index that is designed to  provide exposure to the performance of companies active in copper ore mining that are listed on select North American stock exchanges.
